{"tid":822083,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"岩岩叫麥麥送，仲要冇俾tips送貨仔","createTime":"2018-09-16T07:13:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-17T02:47:18.000Z","uid":171594,"like":17,"dislike":74,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d082cced124520097c7e64689d7919c16bd693b7","tid":822083,"uid":171594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T07:13:46.000Z","msg":"有機會撚班低學歷老麥仔梗係好好把握<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見佢上到黎成身濕撚晒 真係好撚爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要一蚊tips都冇俾佢<br />\n佢原本想找少6毫<br />\n我都問佢攞返<br />\n鬼叫你唔讀書走去做老麥咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇住佢個失落背影就好撚爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87bf287fac2a85598cece7c33fdf1e70bb4a5a17","tid":822083,"uid":27251,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T07:20:44.000Z","msg":"又9up"},{"pid":"70cbe8fa6441c38762f1b7563afe6841862d8484","tid":822083,"uid":134801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T07:24:13.000Z","msg":"55"},{"pid":"35651dcaa325c8a34b76ee159c426f48670265fa","tid":822083,"uid":181905,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T07:24:14.000Z","msg":"公屋仔撚鳩人老麥仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf98ecd41c5ebaa560d75fe4ce404719b3865777","tid":822083,"uid":77461,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T07:24:49.000Z","msg":"頭先叫咗兩份加大餐<br />\n一份留俾外賣仔<br />\n見佢咁辛苦<br />\n叫佢同我一齊食埋先走<br />\n<br />\n利申：冇俾Tips"},{"pid":"a794cbf17dc88b772f226974dc5f9473b53e006d","tid":822083,"uid":35014,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T07:25:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1f9cf8c46834318b0cb18fdd51a6b42e23360a3e","tid":822083,"uid":89931,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy"